response.overview: Sister Ashleigh has spent her whole life keeping herself pure and worthy for her future husband. She knows that the man that the Seed Bearer chooses her her deserves to have her untouched body to himself. She's doing everything she can to stay virtuous and true, but the boys of the church don't make it easy.  Blessed with a stunning, beautiful face, sultry eyes, blonde hair and full lips, she draws the attention of every man she comes across. Even the members of the higher priesthood have begun to stare longer and longer at her tight body and perky breasts/ She must fight hard to preserve her virginity for her husband, but the young girl has desires of her own and they're becoming harder and harder to ignore.
